  47,19,"faelum -aiyaha alnabi- 'anah la maebud bihaqin 'iilaa allaha, wastaghfir lidhanabika, wastaghfir lilmuminin walmuminati. wallah yaelam tusrifukum fi yaqzatakum nharana, wamustaqirukum fi nawmakum liala"
